title: BAYC For ShogunSamurais Fractionalization
body:
This proposal is for all Shogun Medallion holders to have the right to vote on their favourite Bored Ape from the BAYC collection to be fractionalized. Let's welcome a BAYC to the ShogunSamurais Family! 

Below are the #IDs of the BAYC collection up for selection. If the BAYC with the highest vote is sold, we will proceed to purchase the second most voted.

Each Shogun Medallion you hold has ONE weightage in the proposal and you may only select ONE BAYC to vote for
